== Depiction in popular culture ==
Portions of the Apollo 15 mission are dramatized in an episode of the 1998 [[HBO]] miniseries ''[[From the Earth to the Moon (TV miniseries)|From the Earth to the Moon]]'' entitled, "Galileo was Right."

